high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the oven.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle that is on the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Slice the potato that is in the sink basin.
Place the large metal knife into the sink basin tip down in front of the potato.
Pick up the end slice of potato out of the sink.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the microwave.
Open the microwave door and place the slice of potato inside, then microwave it for a couple seconds, after that remove the slice of potato and close the microwave door.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn left again and walk up to the counter, after that look down.
Put the heated slice of potato into the small green bin below the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of potato in a green bin.

high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the black stove top.
Pick up the large knife from the counter next to the stove top.
Turn around, turn to the left, and go to the sink.
Find the potato in the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Continue to slice the potato in the sink.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the potato in the microwave, close the microwave, microwave the potato for two seconds, open the microwave, take the potato out of the microwave, and close the microwave.
Turn to the left, go to the wall, turn to the left, and go to the recycling bin.
Put the potato in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of cooked potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter top located on the left side of the stove.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, turn left then walk towards the sink.
Cut the potato inside of the sink.
Place the knife inside the sink near the potato.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, turn right then walk towards the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the potato slice inside, close the door then turn it on. Open the microwave door, remove the potato slice, then close the door.
Turn left then walk towards the wall, turn left and walk towards the table.
Place the potato slice into the green trash can underneath the table.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a slice of microwaved potato.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the stove.
Pick up the knife next to the stove.
Turn around to go to the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Leave the knife in the sink.
Take one slice of the potato.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave and heat it and take it out.
Turn around to go to the recycling bin.
Put the heated slice of potato in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of a potato into a recycling bin.

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room to face the stove.
Pick up knife to the left of the burners.
Turn left and cross room to the sink, where there is a slice of bread.
Turn the slice of bread so one corner is toward you.
Use the knife to cut the corner off the bread.
Pick up the small piece of bread
Turn right, then right again, and cross room to the microwave.
Put the bread in the microwave and turn microwave on.
Take bread out of the microwave, turn left, turn left, go to the recycling bin.
Throw the piece of bread into the bin.
anns.task_desc: Cook the corner of a slice of bread, then throw it out.
